des:
The “We Buy Houses for Cash” service is provided by real estate investors, who are individual investors that buy houses, or companies that buy houses from people who must have a house sold quickly or with a high level of urgency. 

The Skill can help you understand what how does "We Buy Houses for Cash" services works and can guide you on how to sell your property fast.
